# Project Documentation Search

This project uses `gy-doc-search` to index documentation for AI-assisted development.

## How to Use

- `search_docs(query)` searches across project documentation.
- `get_full_doc(file_path)` reads a relevant file in full.
- `list_doc_sources(prefix)` shows indexed documentation files.
- `doc_index_stats()` reports index coverage and freshness.

## Rules

1. Search for relevant specs before implementing features.
2. Read the full source document when a search result looks relevant.
3. Prefer specific queries and use path filters when you know the area.

